            div(style="margin-top:20px;") Now imagine what could be achieved if other communities had the tools and support to test their ideas through experimentation. There are many people that already collect vast amounts of data about their lives. But what if their tremendous efforts were spent in running scientific experiments - everyday people could be running their own research!

